<h1>Multiple-choice Questions</h1>

<p>This is an application where you can create and answer multiple-choice questions. Anyone using the application can view some basic statistics, including the number of answers and the number of correct answers by the current user, the total number of times the questions created by the current user have been answered, and the five users with the most question answers. In addition, the application also provides an API for retrieving and answering random questions.</p>

<p>If you haven't used the application before, you can start by <a href="/auth/register">registering</a>. If you have been here before, just <a href="/auth/login">log in</a>!</p>

